<br>
The number one thing that seemed to be putting him off the game was the scale of it. Ok, personally i think him having guildchat might have been a mistake, listening to a bunch of 65s whining about PoTa problems probebly is a bit disconcerting when your level 4 and have just been done in by a drowned citizen, but still.<br>
<br>
I honestly dont think the game has got any easier, if anything its got more complex. Focus items, level restrictions, newbie armours, horrably out of date and confusing newspapers. Thers a huge legacy of shit that makes no sense in this game, broken quests, quests that arnt broken but have no point, old style armour dyes...<br>
<br>
PoK is a nightmare, imagine hailing all the fcus item quest people, each requiring 4 stupidly named drops from 4 contenents.... God help you if you write all that down and sit thinking, where the fuck are these places.<br>
<br>
And Griffins in WC, now the tunnel is empty there lethal! Not to mention the joys of your guild telling you to go down a tunnel full of drowned citizens because none of them have a clue what they are as they havent been to freeport since they where added god knows how long ago.<br>
<br>
Hes just reached level eleven now and has learnt a new phrase, &quot;corpse recovery.&quot; Only when we did our first it was against rats in freeport at level 1, we could cope with that. He died in some lucin one we told him was safe and now cant get his corpse back as the lantern he had to buy. (he never got to kill firebeatles, some one took him somewhere more efficent....)<br>
<br>
Ok, hes twinked to high heaven... so what, i started playing just after kunark came out and got twinked by passing strangers... Ok my gear wasent as good, but compartivly it was better... I got an FBR, it was like the 5th best robe you ever saw then, it was awsome, i dident worry about getting a new one till i was past 50.<br>
<br>
Its not simpler, its not easier, its just different... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=malodium>Malodium</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 287<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/9/03 7:48 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ....</span><hr size=1> No matter how easy/hard the game is/was/will be, its not really that that ruins the 'vision'.  Its the hordes of people who get on and just MUST get to level 65 faster than anyone else and get the phattest lewt before anyone else.<br>
