The original team were a little to tight with the reigns, they never seemed to get around to actually fixing/implementing things that really would help the player base.<br>
<br>
 Graveyards = great idea great implementation.<br>
<br>
Mass Transit = good but perhaps should be on a slightly smaller scale.  Say 1 or two books per continant.<br>
<br>
Blass balancing, JFC the onld team totally screwed this up.  They would over power one class a rediculous amount and were so worried about increasing power of another to compensate they either left things alone or nerfed the powerful into the weak.<br>
<br>
The main problem I had with the old eq team is they always had &quot;penalties&quot; for XP, for this or that.  GDI the new team using Bonuses is A-OK with me.  Remember how long it took the old team to admit after two years of people throwing data at them that soloing was preferable to grouping for any class that could solo because you didnt get hit with any penalties nor have to split the xp.<br>
