==============================================<br>
<br>
In total, there was alot finally fixed. but along with the fix they implemented a few small issues that totally offset the way the EQ world worked.<br>
<br>
the way they finally adressed the problems for going into dungeons at lower levels by giving a rez option at lower levels, giving evacuate at lower levels and adding low level corpse summons sure made the game better to those groups. A death would not take the 5 hour it used to take before. and you can bind nearby.<br>
<br>
I like the idea that people below level 46 should consume some item when they want to travel with a book up to the PoK. Or down from the PoK Make it sufficiently expensive, (10pp) and the real newbies are forced to travel the world instead of taking the easy way out. The options that gave EQ its feeling was the huge size of it, and that has been removed <p><center>
